Package net.proteusframework.cms.component.generator

CMS classes for generating content.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cacheable<P extends PageElement>
    Represents something that is responsible for generation or influences the generation of cacheable content.
    DelegateRenderer<T extends PageElement>
    A renderer that is delegated to.
    Generator<T extends PageElement>
    Renderer for content that provides caching information.
    Renderer<T extends PageElement>
    Renderer for content.
    ScriptGenerator<G extends ContentElement>
    Generator interface for scripting component.
    XMLRenderer.Processor
    Processor for XMLGenerator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractScriptGenerator<G extends ContentElement>
    Generator for compilable scripts that implements some methods.
    CacheableBuilder
    Utility to build a cacheable representation of content to be generated.
    ContentWrapper
    Content wrapper for Generators.
    DelegateGenerator<T extends ContentElement>
    Delegate generator.
    GeneratorImpl<PE extends PageElement>
    Generator implementation designed to be extended to protect implementors from API changes.
    IMGTagListener
    Outputs width and height if not specified.
    MIWTGenerator<T extends PageElement>
    Generator for MIWTBean.
    MIWTRenderer<T extends PageElement>
    Renderer for MIWT components.
    ObjectTagListener
    Externalizes media objects and creates image and other types of tags from their internal representation.
    ObjectTagListener.ObjectContext
    Context information.
    PassthroughGenerator<P extends PageElement>
    Generator that calls ProcessChain.processChildElements() and RenderChain.renderChildElements() for all content types.
    SequentialGenerator<P extends PageElement>
    Generator for a list of ContentElements.
    XMLGenerator<T extends ContentElement>
    Simple generator that returns content that is XML fragment.
    XMLRenderer<T extends ContentElement>
    Simple renderer that returns content that is Xml.
